chriebenen Text, wie wir heute wissen.   aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Sep 2018) 4aAthanasius of Alexandria. 4aAthanasius von Alexandrien. 4aCouncil of Florence. 4aFilioque. 4aKonzil von Florenz-Ferrara. 4aKonzilienforschung.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2016z9783110485103oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Theology, Relig. Studies, Jewish Studies 2016z9783110485394oZDB-23-DGF0 cEPUBz97831104686940 cprintz978311045402440uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783110468984423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783110468984.jpg  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA14ALL  aPDA16SSH  aPDA1ALL  aPDA2  aPDA2HUM  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGFb2016  aZDB-23-DGGb2016